{"tid":2392872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"霍建寧傳9億洽售兩大屋  位處舂坎角 呎價近9萬元","createTime":"2021-02-03T05:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T08:34:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"16cdbe0a90e6bcbf554189b092b0ba72f55a1bae","tid":2392872,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:36:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210203/WM3VM2ZVX5DTDIBXUC3MWY3V7E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210203%2FWM3VM2ZVX5DTDIBXUC3MWY3V7E%2F&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrWjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=b7a60241\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210203%2FWM3VM2ZVX5DTDIBXUC3MWY3V7E%2F&h=6df0a01c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210203/WM3VM2ZVX5DTDIBXUC3MWY3V7E/</a><br />\n<br />\n霍建寧傳9億洽售兩大屋 <br />\n位處舂坎角 呎價近9萬元<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】2021年開局，股樓氣氛高漲，九倉（004）、長實（1113）分別推售旗下山頂及西半山豪宅之際，市場傳來「打工皇帝」、長和（001）聯席董事總經理霍建寧持有的赤柱舂坎角道兩間大屋，獲買家出價逾9億元洽購，不排除「霍大班」趁高位沽售貴重物業。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：南區豪宅有價有市<br />\n<br />\n港島南區豪宅供應一向匱乏，擁有無敵海景的赤柱舂坎角道64至66號兩間大屋，乃著名「打工皇帝」霍建寧持有豪宅，曾經自住，隨後轉作收租。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/o6kMXZQWqySMgjhCvzvIVQlJziQ=/1495x777/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UFM2VMNANNCM3JBPVQRB4N7XNQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fo6kMXZQWqySMgjhCvzvIVQlJziQ%3D%2F1495x777%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUFM2VMNANNCM3JBPVQRB4N7XNQ.gif&h=f4755c94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■赤柱舂坎角道64至66號兩間大屋（紅圈示）擁有無敵海景，市傳獲買家出價逾9億元洽購。<br />\n手機用戶請按此放大圖表<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李小加曾是大屋租客<br />\n<br />\n其中，舂坎角道66號，實用面積3,954方呎，建築面積5,285方呎，港交所（388）前行政總裁李小加亦曾是大屋租客。按土地註冊處資料顯示，李小加於2011年至2013年租住該屋，月租28.8萬元，呎租73元；其後，李小加搬遷至大潭龜背灣洋房，而大屋於2015年減租至每月27萬元租予另一位外籍人士，呎租68元。<br />\n<br />\n至於另一幢大屋舂坎角道64號，面積較大，實用面積6,265方呎，2013年獲外籍人士以月租59萬元承租，呎租94元，隨後上調至月租62萬元，呎租99元。<br />\n<br />\n市場消息指，「霍大班」近年。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n兩間屋享有舂坎角海灘景致。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n根據土地註冊處資料，未見霍建寧當年購入舂坎角豪宅作價，有指是1996年以4,200萬元購入，若交易落實，打工皇帝有望賺逾8.5億元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n霍現居深水灣道37號<br />\n<br />\n儘管疫情拖累經濟氣氛轉差，惟超級豪宅未見顯著落價，去年較大額貴重豪宅成交，為香港天主教方濟會會長以8.3億元沽出渣甸山軒德蓀道6號屋地。<br />\n<br />\n此外，理文造紙（2314）主席。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n堪稱李嘉誠「頭馬」的長和大班霍建寧，現。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rnAAca778Yi9IxasLGZCmBbN-68=/720x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MT4V5TOIF5GD7CBXX2RQBYMEZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrnAAca778Yi9IxasLGZCmBbN-68%3D%2F720x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMT4V5TOIF5GD7CBXX2RQBYMEZY.jpg&h=576534a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n霍建寧"},{"pid":"d530e3d79aad06ed2ee93997b150b1c20fa5f6ec","tid":2392872,"uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:37:55.000Z","msg":"賣咗用首置身份再買免稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d986a802cddac48925d94331af731e3d5414262","tid":2392872,"uid":108201,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:41:06.000Z","msg":"跟誠哥一齊走資<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d778d3af64db168af06aa14699d9990ba9ea9f8c","tid":2392872,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:42:11.000Z","msg":"開始走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deff3e2c7b6eb12b0b6ccf464609ed455904848f","tid":2392872,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:42:35.000Z","msg":"打工皇帝真係唔同d"},{"pid":"c46534eea95fe85e50f1096f0fdf3bf2cafd5823","tid":2392872,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:42:39.000Z","msg":"老鳩走得